txt.en: Ereblen can be found at Echad Uial.\n\nYou should bring the additional supplies to Ereblen.
Additional supplies can be found within the Harrowing of Morgul.\n\nYou should gather any additional supplies that you find.
'The harrowing of Minas Morgul is upon us, [placeholder]. Perhaps the conflict within the city is just the opportunity to retrieve some additional supplies. Will you assist us?'
There is much for the White Company to accomplish in reclaiming Minas Ithil from the remnants of Sauron's forces.
'I see that you have succeeded! These supplies will do well. Thank you, [placeholder]. You have done Gondor a great service today.'
